---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Logo from "../components/Logo.astro";
import ConeChart from "../components/ConeChart.astro";
import SynergyAd from "../components/SynergyAd.astro";

const year = new Date().getFullYear();

// The manifesto, essay by essay. Bodies may carry inline markup; an optional
// `finale` renders as an embellished closing flourish.
const essays: { title: string; body: string; finale?: string }[] = [
  {
    title: "FrAgile",
    body: `Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec lacinia iaculis ultricies. Morbi non dictum neque, vel commodo erat. Praesent placerat libero at nisl efficitur tristique. Vivamus id nulla a nibh euismod eleifend. Etiam malesuada lectus sit amet eros semper, at fringilla lorem malesuada. Curabitur faucibus pellentesque lacinia. This sums up <em>&ldquo;agile&rdquo;</em> well enough.`,
  },
  {
    title: "Use the Uppercase-A Agile",
    body: `I used to use &ldquo;Agile.&rdquo; Then I used &ldquo;agile.&rdquo; Now I no longer use the word at all. It started as a principle, it endured as a buzzword, and it ended on the tail end of a fad. Now it comes with a certification and a laminated card.`,
  },
  {
    title: "Who&rsquo;s update is it anyway?",
    body: `<p>Let&rsquo;s see, I went to a bunch of meetings, looked at incomplete and poorly written <em>&ldquo;stories&rdquo;</em> and I restarted my computer six times for no reason. No blockers, well, except this meeting.</p>
    <p>Standup is for telling folks what you&rsquo;re doing right now and what you might work on shortly. It&rsquo;s not a race, it&rsquo;s not a competition, it&rsquo;s not a game. It&rsquo;s a brief nexus to coordinate, it&rsquo;s a place for a humble plea for help.</p>
    <p>It&rsquo;s the show where everything&rsquo;s made up and the points don&rsquo;t matter.</p>`,
  },
  {
    title: "Points and Pineapples",
    body: `Points are silly. Work is not continuous. Teams are not uniform. Knowledge is not yet learned, expertise is not yet felt. Points are a desperate plea to commoditize the so-called delivery of software. How many points did you do this sprint? More? Awesome. Less? Grossly unacceptable. The discussion of value and the exploration of problem and solution space, that&rsquo;s what is important here. Points are not. Next sprint we&rsquo;re estimating in pineapples &mdash; just as accurate, twice as fun.`,
  },
  {
    title: "Distributed Dysfunction&trade;",
    body: `Who made these choices? Who are any of you? How could you do this? Let&rsquo;s find out. The org chart is eventually consistent; the blame replicates instantly.`,
  },
  {
    title: "Architectural Faffery",
    body: `It&rsquo;s not intellectual faffery, but it might as well be. It&rsquo;s when you decide that an interesting architecture matters more than the product in someone&rsquo;s hands or it even working. By all means, use your service discovery queue mesh distributed scalable serverless PaaS. But before you do, let&rsquo;s consider the facts. You have four users. Two of them are you.`,
  },
  {
    title: "The Entropy Builds Up",
    body: `You listen to customers. You build what they want. You build what they need. You keep chasing the dream. Suddenly, your system is broken and you have nowhere left to turn. What went wrong? Entropy begins and ends all things. The burndown chart, it turns out, only ever burns up.`,
  },
  {
    title: "There are no 4&rsquo;s in the Serengeti",
    body: `Right angles are boring; nature never drew one. Yet somewhere an analyst has trapped your entire industry inside a four-box grid &mdash; Leaders, Challengers, Visionaries, and whatever corner they dropped you in &mdash; and called it a Magic Quadrant. There are no quadrants on the savanna. The Serengeti counts in spirals: one, one, two, three, five, eight. Notice what&rsquo;s missing? Four. Four is too comfortable, too certain, too square.`,
  },
  {
    title: "We&rsquo;re in a state of Jabberwocky",
    body: `We&rsquo;ve got the product you&rsquo;ve always wanted. All you have to do is believe. And don&rsquo;t do your research. The roadmap gyres, the KPIs gimble, and somewhere a stakeholder cries &ldquo;callooh, callay!&rdquo; Ship it.`,
  },
  {
    title: "End of the line",
    body: `The gist is, my dear reader, that agile is four simple preferences. That&rsquo;s it. Everything you ever learned, everything you thought you knew, everything you thought you were waiting to discover &mdash; it was all false. If all that specialization were the natural order, the specialization would not exist or be necessary. And it&rsquo;s not. The natural order is the end of the line: go and do the work.`,
    finale: `Let&rsquo;s prevent the <span class="finale__phrase">devastated wasteland</span> together.`,
  },
];

const pad = (n: number) => String(n).padStart(2, "0");
---

<Layout>
  <!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
  <header class="hero">
    <div class="hero__bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="hero__scrim" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="hero__inner">
      <div class="hero__mark"><Logo /></div>
      <h1 class="hero__title brand">devastated<br />wasteland</h1>
      <div class="hero__meta">
        <span class="hero__soon">Coming soon</span>
        <span class="hero__year">{year}</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="#manifesto" class="hero__scroll" aria-label="Scroll to the manifesto">
      <span class="hero__scroll-label">Enter the wasteland</span>
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" aria-hidden="true">
        <path
          d="M12 4v15m0 0l-6-6m6 6l6-6"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="1.6"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
      </svg>
    </a>
  </header>

  <!-- ============ BODY ============ -->
  <main id="manifesto" class="page">
    <!-- Colophon -->
    <section class="colophon reveal">
      <p class="kicker">Why &ldquo;devastated wasteland&rdquo;?</p>
      <p class="colophon__lede">
        <a href="https://www.kentbeck.com/">Kent Beck</a>, a signer of the
        <a href="https://agilemanifesto.org/">legendary agile manifesto</a>,
        responded with this phrase during
        <a
          rel="noreferrer noopener"
          target="_blank"
          href="https://builtin.com/software-engineering-perspectives/kent-beck-geeks-gusto-globalization#:~:text=It%E2%80%99s%20a%20devastated%20wasteland."
          >an interview in 2020</a
        >. It&rsquo;s an evocative phrase, perfectly placed to get a reader riled
        up and engaged with the purpose of these processes, practices and
        principles.
      </p>

      <blockquote class="quote">
        <p class="quote__q">
          You signed the Agile Manifesto almost 20 years ago. How do you feel
          about agile now?
        </p>
        <p class="quote__a">
          It&rsquo;s a <strong>devastated wasteland</strong>. The life has been
          sucked out of it. It&rsquo;s a few religious rituals carried out by
          people who don&rsquo;t understand the purpose that those rituals were
          intended to serve in the first place.
        </p>
        <cite class="quote__cite">— Kent Beck</cite>
      </blockquote>
    </section>

    <div class="rule reveal" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <!-- Essays, with the cone ad wedged in as an interstitial -->
    <div class="essays">
      {
        essays.map((essay, i) => (
          <>
            <article class="essay reveal">
              <span class="essay__num" aria-hidden="true">
                {pad(i + 1)}
              </span>
              <div class="essay__content">
                <h2 class="essay__title" set:html={essay.title} />
                <div class="essay__body" set:html={essay.body} />
                {
                  essay.finale && (
                    <div class="finale">
                      <span class="finale__rule" aria-hidden="true" />
                      <p class="finale__text" set:html={essay.finale} />
                    </div>
                  )
                }
              </div>
            </article>
            {i === 1 && <SynergyAd />}
            {i === 4 && <ConeChart />}
          </>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- ============ FOOTER ============ -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer__mark"><Logo /></div>
    <p class="footer__brand brand">devastated wasteland</p>
    <p class="footer__credit">
      Photo by
      <a rel="noreferrer noopener" target="_blank" href="https://unsplash.com/@jverdi"
        >Jared Verdi</a
      >
      on
      <a
        rel="noreferrer noopener"
        target="_blank"
        href="https://unsplash.com/photos/PNKwdJ8WetM">Unsplash</a
      >
    </p>
    <p class="footer__year">{year}</p>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* ---------------- HERO ---------------- */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100svh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: var(--edge);
  }

  .hero__bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("/assets/images/bg-1.jpeg");
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    /* duotone the photo toward the ashscape — kept legible, imagery intentional */
    filter: grayscale(0.2) contrast(1.04) brightness(0.68) sepia(0.16)
      hue-rotate(-14deg) saturate(1.02);
    transform: scale(1.06);
    animation: drift 32s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }

  .hero__scrim {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(
        125% 95% at 50% 32%,
        transparent 0%,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--void) 38%, transparent) 58%,
        var(--void) 100%
      ),
      linear-gradient(
        to bottom,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--void) 30%, transparent) 0%,
        transparent 34%,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--void) 52%, transparent) 80%,
        var(--void) 100%
      );
  }

  @keyframes drift {
    from {
      transform: scale(1.06) translate3d(-1.2%, -1%, 0);
    }
    to {
      transform: scale(1.12) translate3d(1.2%, 1%, 0);
    }
  }

  .hero__inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero__mark {
    width: clamp(6rem, 13vw, 9rem);
    color: var(--bone);
    filter: drop-shadow(0 6px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6));
    animation: rise 1s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) both;
  }

  .hero__mark :global(svg) {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    animation: spin 22s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes spin {
    to {
      transform: rotate(360deg);
    }
  }

  .hero__title {
    margin: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3rem) 0 0;
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 11vw, 8rem);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    color: var(--bone);
    text-shadow:
      0 0 28px color-mix(in srgb, var(--rust) 45%, transparent),
      0 2px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    animation: rise 1s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.12s both;
  }

  .hero__meta {
    margin-top: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    animation: rise 1s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.24s both;
  }

  .hero__soon {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.42em;
    font-size: clamp(0.85rem, 2vw, 1.05rem);
    color: var(--bone);
    padding-left: 0.42em;
  }

  .hero__year {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--rust-bright);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    padding-left: 0.3em;
  }

  @keyframes rise {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(1.5rem);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: none;
    }
  }

  .hero__scroll {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: clamp(1.5rem, 4vh, 2.75rem);
    /* center without transform — the rise animation owns transform */
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    margin-inline: auto;
    width: max-content;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    border: none;
    color: var(--bone-dim);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-align: center;
    animation: rise 1s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.5s both;
  }

  .hero__scroll-label {
    letter-spacing: 0.24em;
    /* offset the trailing letter-spacing so the text is optically centered */
    padding-left: 0.24em;
  }

  .hero__scroll:hover {
    background: none;
    color: var(--rust-bright);
  }

  .hero__scroll svg {
    animation: bob 2.2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes bob {
    0%,
    100% {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(4px);
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .hero__bg,
    .hero__mark,
    .hero__mark :global(svg),
    .hero__scroll svg,
    .hero__title,
    .hero__meta,
    .hero__scroll {
      animation: none;
    }
  }

  /* ---------------- PAGE ---------------- */
  .page {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: var(--measure);
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 8rem) var(--edge) 0;
  }

  .colophon__lede {
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2vw, 1.4rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 1rem 0 0;
    color: var(--bone);
  }

  .quote {
    margin: 3rem 0 0;
    padding: 1.75rem 0 1.75rem 2rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--rust);
  }

  .quote__q {
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    color: var(--bone-dim);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .quote__a {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 3vw, 1.85rem);
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: var(--bone);
  }

  .quote__cite {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--bone-faint);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .rule {
    height: 1px;
    margin: clamp(4rem, 9vw, 6.5rem) 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to right,
      transparent,
      var(--ash-600) 12%,
      var(--ash-600) 88%,
      transparent
    );
  }

  /* ---------------- ESSAYS ---------------- */
  .essays {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: clamp(3.5rem, 8vw, 5.5rem);
  }

  .essay {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(2.5rem, auto) 1fr;
    gap: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .essay__num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding-top: 0.55rem;
    color: var(--rust);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .essay__title {
    margin: 0 0 0.9rem;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 4.5vw, 2.6rem);
    line-height: 1.12;
    color: var(--bone);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .essay__body :global(p) {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .essay__body :global(p:last-child) {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 34rem) {
    .essay {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .essay__num {
      padding-top: 0;
    }
  }

  /* ---------------- FINALE ---------------- */
  .finale {
    margin-top: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
  }

  .finale__rule {
    display: block;
    width: 3rem;
    height: 2px;
    margin-bottom: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 1.75rem);
    background: var(--rust);
    box-shadow: 0 0 14px color-mix(in srgb, var(--rust) 70%, transparent);
  }

  .finale__text {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(1.65rem, 5vw, 2.9rem);
    line-height: 1.22;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--bone);
  }

  .finale__text :global(.finale__phrase) {
    color: var(--rust-bright);
    text-shadow: 0 0 24px color-mix(in srgb, var(--rust) 55%, transparent);
    animation: finaleGlow 3.6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes finaleGlow {
    0%,
    100% {
      text-shadow: 0 0 16px color-mix(in srgb, var(--rust) 40%, transparent);
    }
    50% {
      text-shadow: 0 0 34px color-mix(in srgb, var(--rust) 80%, transparent);
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .finale__text :global(.finale__phrase) {
      animation: none;
    }
  }

  /* ---------------- FOOTER ---------------- */
  .footer {
    margin-top: clamp(5rem, 12vw, 9rem);
    padding: clamp(4rem, 9vw, 7rem) var(--edge) clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5rem);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ash-700);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 1.1rem;
  }

  .footer__mark {
    width: 3.4rem;
    color: var(--bone-dim);
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .footer__mark :global(svg) {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  .footer__brand {
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 3vw, 1.5rem);
    color: var(--bone);
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .footer__credit {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--bone-dim);
  }

  .footer__year {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--bone-faint);
  }
</style>
